c=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"白字係上網搵 紅字先係我講嘅嘢"},{"pid":"b19990c8b7566801b01afe8936c91a8b6b00f95c","tid":926125,"uid":202674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"神真係可以&ldquo;論證&ldquo;到存唔存在咩？我覺得宗教從來都唔係講證據，或者邏輯，係講見證既。而見證係一樣好個人既野黎，好難可以用黎論證。<br />\n宗教講既係信心，唔係邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔係話宗教可笑，只係如果用科學角度討論，可能搵唔到樓主想要既答案。<br />\n<br />\n咁就好似想去利用科學會解釋宇宙存在既意義，我地可能可以搵到宇宙起源，甚至證明到宇宙大爆炸既理論，但係科學好難去解釋點解宇宙需要存在。如果因為科學難以解釋而去dismiss宇宙本身既意義既話，其實係好唔符合科學精神。"},{"pid":"35df0b7c599339f1572db092640ac3a44fabfc37","tid":926125,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"有掛，咩都有可能㗎啦"},{"pid":"55493226659192c1ec670d43cef48f496a93829b","tid":926125,"uid":59179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc156fb2ea74d4c34c33d30b28788a0378b8d3e","tid":926125,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"158e27f0f6fed41375b2b1dd1fad2b63064c8319","tid":926125,"uid":213441,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"咁神由咩推動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"所以壽提出係一切之源"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"何謂一切 神唔歸類為一切裏面？"},{"pid":"8cdd101494be94c94ffe3eabee5b67f2d69ef79b","tid":926125,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ouReaSsQbU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DouReaSsQbU8&d=XujJ2F4hOZH7RZ%2F1MvXa7jANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=df06439d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ouReaSsQbU8</a><br />\n<br />\n《宇宙論證─神是存在的嗎？》<br />\n<br />\nKalam cosmological argument<br />\n<br />\n1: Whatever begins to exist has a cause.<br />\n<br />\n2: The universe began to exist.<br />\n<br />\n3: Therefore, the universe has a cause.<br />\n<br />\n4: If th